sub_title: Manager Frontoffice & Sales Support (Germany) at Norah
summary:
An ambitious and energetic person with a healthy drive to perform and book results. As people manager I am an initiator, decisive and able to prioritize. I am a team player but also a team builder.
Due to my language skills I feel at home in an international company in a multicultural environment.
Experience as backoffice manager, customer service employee for shoe industry, fashion, cosmetics and industrial doors/technical company.
Sap customer master data specialist.
German native speaker
